-- 
Shell to Sell Stanlow Refinery to Essar Energy, Mail Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-03-20T21:48:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-20/shell-to-sell-stanlow-refinery-to-essar-energy-mail-reports.html
  Royal Dutch Shell Plc (RDSA)  is to sell
its Stanlow oil refinery in the U.K to  Essar Energy Plc (ESSR)  for 217
million pounds ($352 million), the  Mail on Sunday  reported,
without citing a source for the information. The oil and
gasoline in the refinery will be bought separately for almost
500 million pounds, the newspaper reported.  A Shell spokesman declined to comment when contacted by
telephone.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 